---

<html lang="ko">
	<head>
		<meta charset="utf-8" />
		<title>유형 01[하] 10문항 문제지 미리보기 (5페이지)</title>
		<link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/katex@0.16.11/dist/katex.min.css">
		<script is:inline src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/katex@0.16.11/dist/katex.min.js"></script>
		<script is:inline src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/katex@0.16.11/dist/contrib/auto-render.min.js"></script>
		<style>
			@import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Serif+KR:wght@310;400;700&display=swap');

			body {
				background-color: #525659;
				margin: 0;
				padding: 50px 0;
				display: flex;
				flex-direction: column;
				align-items: center;
				font-family: 'Noto Serif KR', serif;
				gap: 40px;
			}

			.a4-page {
				background: white;
				width: 210mm;
				height: 297mm;
				padding: 20mm;
				box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.4);
				box-sizing: border-box;
				position: relative;
				display: flex;
				flex-direction: column;
			}

			.page-number {
				position: absolute;
				bottom: 15mm;
				left: 0;
				right: 0;
				text-align: center;
				font-size: 10pt;
				color: #888;
			}

			.exam-header {
				text-align: center;
				margin-bottom: 20px;
				border-bottom: 2px solid black;
				padding-bottom: 10px;
			}

			.exam-title { font-size: 18pt; font-weight: 700; margin: 0; }
			.exam-subtitle { font-size: 14pt; font-weight: 700; margin: 5px 0; }

			.info-box {
				border: 1px solid black;
				padding: 8px;
				display: grid;
				grid-template-columns: 1.5fr 1fr;
				font-size: 10pt;
				margin-bottom: 30px;
			}

			.exam-content {
				display: grid;
				grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
				column-gap: 50px;
				flex-grow: 1;
				position: relative;
			}

			.exam-content::after {
				content: '';
				position: absolute;
				left: 50%;
				top: 0;
				bottom: 0;
				width: 1px;
				background: #eee;
			}

			.problem {
				margin-bottom: 50px;
				line-height: 1.8;
				font-size: 11pt;
				min-height: 300px;
			}

			.prob-num { font-weight: 700; font-size: 1.2em; margin-right: 8px; }
			.score { font-size: 9pt; float: right; margin-top: 4px; color: #666; }
			.formula-display { text-align: center; margin: 30px 0; font-size: 1.2em; }
			
			.workspace-hint {
				border: 1px dashed #eee;
				height: 200px;
				margin-top: 20px;
				display: flex;
				align-items: center;
				justify-content: center;
				color: #ccc;
				font-size: 9pt;
				font-style: italic;
			}
		</style>
	</head>
	<body>

		<!-- Page 1: Q1, Q2 -->
		<div class="a4-page">
			<div class="exam-header">
				<p class="exam-title">2027학년도 대학수학능력시험 대비 핵심 문제집</p>
				<p class="exam-subtitle">유형 01. 극한값의 기본 계산 [하]</p>
			</div>
			<div class="info-box">
				<div><b>단위 단원:</b> 01. 함수의 극한과 연속</div>
				<div style="text-align: right;"><b>성명:</b> ____________________</div>
			</div>
			<div class="exam-content">
				<div class="col">
					<div class="problem">
						<span class="score">(2점)</span>
						<span class="prob-num">1.</span>
						다음 극한값을 구하시오.
						<div class="formula-display">$$ \lim_{x \to 2} (3x - 1) $$</div>
						<div class="workspace-hint">(풀이 공간)</div>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="col">
					<div class="problem">
						<span class="score">(2점)</span>
						<span class="prob-num">2.</span>
						다음 극한값을 구하시오.
						<div class="formula-display">$$ \lim_{x \to 1} (x^2 + 2x + 3) $$</div>
						<div class="workspace-hint">(풀이 공간)</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="page-number">- 1 -</div>
		</div>

		<!-- Page 2: Q3, Q4 -->
		<div class="a4-page">
			<div class="exam-content">
				<div class="col">
					<div class="problem">
						<span class="score">(3점)</span>
						<span class="prob-num">3.</span>
						다음 극한값을 구하시오.
						<div class="formula-display">$$ \lim_{x \to 3} \frac{x^2 - 9}{x - 3} $$</div>
						<div class="workspace-hint"></div>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="col">
					<div class="problem">
						<span class="score">(3점)</span>
						<span class="prob-num">4.</span>
						다음 극한값을 구하시오.
						<div class="formula-display">$$ \lim_{x \to -1} \frac{x + 1}{x^2 - 1} $$</div>
						<div class="workspace-hint"></div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="page-number">- 2 -</div>
		</div>

		<!-- Page 3: Q5, Q6 -->
		<div class="a4-page">
			<div class="exam-content">
				<div class="col">
					<div class="problem">
						<span class="score">(3점)</span>
						<span class="prob-num">5.</span>
						다음 극한값을 구하시오.
						<div class="formula-display">$$ \lim_{x \to 0} \frac{2x^2 + x}{x} $$</div>
						<div class="workspace-hint"></div>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="col">
					<div class="problem">
						<span class="score">(3점)</span>
						<span class="prob-num">6.</span>
						다음 극한값을 구하시오.
						<div class="formula-display">$$ \lim_{x \to 4} \frac{\sqrt{x} - 2}{x - 4} $$</div>
						<div class="workspace-hint"></div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="page-number">- 3 -</div>
		</div>

		<!-- Page 4: Q7, Q8 -->
		<div class="a4-page">
			<div class="exam-content">
				<div class="col">
					<div class="problem">
						<span class="score">(3점)</span>
						<span class="prob-num">7.</span>
						다음 극한값을 구하시오.
						<div class="formula-display">$$ \lim_{x \to 1} \frac{1 - x}{1 - \sqrt{x}} $$</div>
						<div class="workspace-hint"></div>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="col">
					<div class="problem">
						<span class="score">(4점)</span>
						<span class="prob-num">8.</span>
						다음 극한값을 구하시오.
						<div class="formula-display">$$ \lim_{x \to \infty} \frac{3x + 1}{2x - 5} $$</div>
						<div class="workspace-hint"></div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="page-number">- 4 -</div>
		</div>

		<!-- Page 5: Q9, Q10 -->
		<div class="a4-page">
			<div class="exam-content">
				<div class="col">
					<div class="problem">
						<span class="score">(4점)</span>
						<span class="prob-num">9.</span>
						다음 극한값을 구하시오.
						<div class="formula-display">$$ \lim_{x \to \infty} \frac{2x^2 - x}{x^2 + 3} $$</div>
						<div class="workspace-hint"></div>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="col">
					<div class="problem">
						<span class="score">(4점)</span>
						<span class="prob-num">10.</span>
						다음 극한값을 구하시오.
						<div class="formula-display">$$ \lim_{x \to -\infty} (\sqrt{x^2 + 2x} + x) $$</div>
						<div class="workspace-hint"></div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="page-number">- 5 -</div>
		</div>

		<script is:inline>
			document.addEventListener("DOMContentLoaded", function() {
				renderMathInElement(document.body, {
					delimiters: [
						{left: '$$', right: '$$', display: true},
						{left: '$', right: '$', display: false}
					],
					throwOnError : false
				});
			});
		</script>
	</body>
</html>
